OL,3,CRegulator announces crackdown on vape
OL,4,Cads across social media
OL,6,FVape ads across social media "need to
OL,7,Fstop" and ignorance on the part of
OL,8,Fadvertisers is not an excuse, the
OL,9,Fregulator has warned.
OL,11,FThe Committee of Advertising Practice
OL,12,F(Cap) has launched a crackdown on vape
OL,13,Fadvertisers, warning the law prohibits
OL,14,Fthem from marketing e-cigarettes
OL,15,Fcontaining nicotine that are not
OL,16,Flicensed as medicines on most social
OL,17,Fmedia.
