OL,3,CRegulator announces crackdown on vape
OL,4,Cads across social media
OL,6,FRetailers are prohibited from selling
OL,7,Fe-cigarettes or vapes to under-18s and
OL,8,Fthe devices can therefore not be
OL,9,Fadvertised across almost all media, or
OL,10,Fbe targeted at children.
OL,12,FThis means brands or retailers cannot
OL,13,Fpromote them in paid-for posts or in
OL,14,Fnon-paid-for posts on non-private
OL,15,Faccounts, such as on TikTok, Instagram
OL,16,For Facebook.
