OL,3,CRegulator announces crackdown on vape
OL,4,Cads across social media
OL,6,FIn the few spaces where ads for vapes
OL,7,Fare allowed, such as on company
OL,8,Fwebsites, they must not be targeted or
OL,9,Fappeal particularly to under-18s and
OL,10,Fcan only contain factual claims about
OL,11,Fproducts.
OL,13,FCap said it had sent an enforcement
OL,14,Fnotice to e-cigarette manufacturers
OL,15,Fand retailers, making the rules clear
OL,16,Fand emphasising that ignorance is not
OL,17,Fan excuse, adding: "We won't hesitate
OL,18,Fto apply sanctions against advertisers
OL,19,Fwho are either unwilling or unable to
OL,20,Fcomply."
