OL,3,CRegulator announces crackdown on vape
OL,4,Cads across social media
OL,6,FAdvertisers have until March 28 to
OL,7,Fmake sure their ads are compliant.
OL,8,FFollowing this, Cap said it will be
OL,9,Fcarrying out enhanced monitoring and
OL,10,Fwould take action if it found ads that
OL,11,Fwere breaking the rules.
OL,13,FLast year, Cap issued an enforcement
OL,14,Fnotice to e-cigarette manufacturers
OL,15,Fand retailers requiring them to stop
OL,16,Fpaid promotions on TikTok.
