OL,3,CRegulator announces crackdown on vape
OL,4,Cads across social media
OL,6,FCap secretary Shahriar Coupal said:
OL,7,F"The law prohibits e-cigarette ads
OL,8,Fappearing on most social media
OL,9,Faccounts, so it's simply unacceptable
OL,10,Ffor companies to advertise in these
OL,11,Fspaces.
OL,13,F"AI-assisted monitoring tells us that
OL,14,Fthese companies are typically small
OL,15,Ftraders promoting e-cigarettes through
OL,16,Ftheir social media accounts or
OL,17,Fincentivising others to do so, most
OL,18,Flikely in ignorance of our rules and
OL,19,Fthe law.
