OL,4,Cads across social media
OL,6,F"Our enforcement notice leaves traders
OL,7,Fin no doubt about their obligations
OL,8,Funder both and makes clear that e-
OL,9,Fcigarette promotions through social
OL,10,Fmedia channels need to stop.
OL,12,F"For those that fail to do so, we and
OL,13,Four enforcement partners won't
OL,14,Fhesitate to sanction them."
